timelineItems.desc: Dan Haiek and Armchair Analyst Matt Doyle preview the Saturday evening match between the Philadelphia Union and Vancouver Whitecaps. Can the Union record another shutout? Will the Philly attackers exploit gaps in the Vancouver defense? Find out Saturday at 7pm ET on MLS Live.
